The new Toyota Mirai is looking to the
future with sustainability in mind,

00:03:41.489 --> 00:03:45.389
fueled by hydrogen and leaving
zero-emissions behind. Now that California

00:03:45.389 --> 00:03:48.180
and other southwestern regions are
beginning to react to this massive

00:03:48.180 --> 00:03:51.359
drought, chances are we'll see more
native plants and landscaping that

00:03:51.359 --> 00:03:55.440
require less water and are more suited
to our habitat. That's probably good.

